                            <comment id="12858116" author="ryanobjc" created="Sat, 17 Apr 2010 09:00:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;generally i would avoid putting in explicit NPE checks if they were going to fail 1 or 2 lines later. moar code is badddd&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
